# Frontend Architecture

Stack: React 19, Vite, React Router.

Pattern: **Pages + Features + Services** (mirrors backend feature folders with a thin HTTP layer).

## Folder structure

```
frontend/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ src/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ main.jsx                    # entry point
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ App.jsx                     # root layout + router outlet
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ app/                        # bootstrap (no UI)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ router.jsx              # route definitions
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ providers.jsx           # context providers (auth, theme, etc.)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ pages/                      # route-level screens вҖ” thin, compose features
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ login/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ LoginPage.jsx
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ register/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ RegisterPage.jsx
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ chat/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ ChatPage.jsx
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ features/                   # domain UI + hooks grouped by feature
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ auth/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ components/         # LoginForm, RegisterForm, etc.
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ hooks/              # useAuth, useLogin, etc.
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ chat/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ components/         # ChatWindow, MessageList, MessageInput
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ hooks/              # useChat, useMessages, etc.
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ components/                 # shared UI not tied to one feature
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ ui/                     # Button, Input, Spinner, etc.
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
