в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ index.html
в”ңв”Җв”Җ vite.config.js
в””в”Җв”Җ package.json
```

## Layer responsibilities

| Layer | Responsibility | Depends on |
|-------|----------------|------------|
| `app/router.jsx` | Route map, lazy loading, protected routes | `pages/` |
| `app/providers.jsx` | Wraps app with AuthProvider and other contexts | `features/*/hooks` |
| `pages/` | One screen per route; wires feature components together | `features/`, `components/` |
| `features/<domain>/` | Domain-specific UI, local state, feature hooks | `services/`, `components/ui` |
| `components/ui/` | Reusable presentational components | nothing domain-specific |
| `services/` | API calls to backend (`/api/v1/...`); no React | `lib/env` |
| `hooks/` | Shared hooks used by multiple features | varies |
| `lib/` | Pure utilities, env validation | env vars |

## Request flow

```
Page вҶ’ feature component/hook вҶ’ service вҶ’ backend API
                вҶҳ components/ui (presentational)
```

## Routes (initial)

| Path | Page | Access |
|------|------|--------|
| `/login` | `LoginPage` | public |
| `/register` | `RegisterPage` | public |
| `/chat` | `ChatPage` | authenticated |
| `/` | redirect to `/chat` or `/login` | вҖ” |

## Design rules

1. **Thin pages** вҖ” pages compose features; no fetch logic or heavy state in `pages/`
2. **Feature colocation** вҖ” auth UI/hooks live under `features/auth/`, chat under `features/chat/`
3. **Services own HTTP** вҖ” all `fetch` calls go through `services/`; components and hooks call services
4. **Shared UI only in `components/ui/`** вҖ” feature-specific markup stays in `features/<domain>/components/`
5. **Env in one place** вҖ” read `import.meta.env` only in `lib/env.js`
6. **No business rules in services** вҖ” services map request/response; validation and orchestration live in hooks or backend

## Where to put new code

- New route/screen вҶ’ `pages/<name>/<Name>Page.jsx` + register in `app/router.jsx`
- Auth UI or hook вҶ’ `features/auth/`
- Chat UI or hook вҶ’ `features/chat/`
- Reusable button/input/layout вҶ’ `components/ui/`
- New API integration вҶ’ `services/<domain>Service.js`
- Shared hook вҶ’ `hooks/`
- Utility / constant вҶ’ `lib/`
